cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving language modeling using a novel architecture for recurrent neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the reduction of parameters and the use of skip connections, which are common topics in machine learning and deep learning research. Therefore, the other likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
